body:
Which version of OS X are you running? On closer inspection of your first screenshot, the error message is:

```
Symbol not found: ___sincos_stret
```

Looking [elsewhere](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/25926495/symbol-not-found-sincos-stret) suggests that this symbol is only available in OS X 10.9 and above.
